data.title: Marines TV
meta_keywords: Combined Joint Task Force-Operation Inherent Resolve
data.meta_description: U.S Marines assigned to SPMAGTF CR-RR 20.2, discuss what its like to be from the same place and deploy together to the same place. The SPMAGTF-CR-CC is a crisis response force, prepared to mobilize a variety of capabilities across the region. (U.S. Marine Corps Photo by Cpl. Robert Kuehn)
